Former Big Brother Naija housemate, Khloe Abiri, has revealed that she is in need of a rich man to marry her as she is growing older. The BBN Star disclosed this on Wednesday via her Instagram story, expressing that she can never marry a poor man She wrote, I’m gonna be super blunt and honest here and throw all of my shit out there. I won’t be upset if after this all this men in my dm run the other way. I’m not into playing around. l’Il be 29 this year. I don’t have time for childish games. “I need a MAN who will love me no matter what!! I need someone who will tell me how they’re feeling and let me express the same feelings without getting pissed off at me for feeling some type of way. I need a man who will be a father figure to my children. (In due time, obviously). “Someone they can look up to in life, show them how to treat a woman. I want someone who will kiss me, hug me, and love me without me having to ask for it. I’m over wasting my time on fucking around, I don’t want that.I want to find my person. “And i’m sorry i won’t interact with a broke man .. call me gold digger all you want but Remember i’m not broke and i can afford all i want and more so we gotta stay rich together or you rich rich and elevate me.”